      <title>欧盟发誓要与特朗普20％的关税做出对策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/eu-vows-to-respond-with-countermeasures-to-trump-s-20-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大的贸易伙伴欧盟发誓要进行报复，此前唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）宣布对集团的征收关税，以拆除全球贸易体系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/eu-vows-to-respond-with-countermeasures-to-trump-s-20-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 03:27:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国总理说准备应对美国关税，计划会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/thailand-pm-says-prepared-to-deal-with-us-tariffs-plans-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理佩顿顿·辛瓦瓦特拉（Paetongtarn Shinawatra）表示，泰国准备应对特朗普政府征收的36％所谓的相互关税的后果，并补充说，东南亚国家将与美国举行会谈，以降低征税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/thailand-pm-says-prepared-to-deal-with-us-tariffs-plans-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 03:00:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>起亚首席执行官在特朗普的关税云美国观点时向欧洲看</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/kia-ceo-looks-to-europe-as-trump-s-tariffs-cloud-us-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[起亚公司的目标是在唐纳德·特朗普总统的汽车关税和反越门政策中销售欧洲更多的电动汽车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/kia-ceo-looks-to-europe-as-trump-s-tariffs-cloud-us-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 02:55:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本称特朗普对24％的关税感到遗憾，推动豁免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/japan-calls-trump-s-24-tariff-regrettable-pushes-for-exemption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本贸易部长表示，在美国在日本宣布新的税款高于预期之后数小时，特朗普政府的最新关税宽边是非常遗憾的，并予以豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/japan-calls-trump-s-24-tariff-regrettable-pushes-for-exemption</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 02:37:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对印度的“朋友”莫迪的压力为26％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-piles-pressure-on-friend-modi-with-26-tariff-on-india</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统以对美国任何主要贸易伙伴征收的一些最高关税利率拍打印度，称他与总理纳伦德拉·莫迪（Narendra Modi）的良好联系并没有影响他的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-piles-pressure-on-friend-modi-with-26-tariff-on-india</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:32:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>RBA认为银行对美国关税的寒冷效果有弹性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/rba-sees-banks-as-resilient-to-chilling-effect-of-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[储备银行在半年的审查中说，尽管澳大利亚的金融体系非常适合环境风暴，但美国贸易政策和国家对它们的反应可能会对全球商业投资和家庭支出产生“令人不寒而栗的影响”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/rba-sees-banks-as-resilient-to-chilling-effect-of-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国举行紧急会议以应对关税危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-korea-holds-emergency-meeting-to-cope-with-tariff-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在特朗普政府宣布遇到美国安全盟友的最糟糕的关税率之一之后，韩国的临时领导层被置于紧急模式，以保护依靠出口的经济免受贸易危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-korea-holds-emergency-meeting-to-cope-with-tariff-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:10:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南魅力攻势未能避免46％的特朗普关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/vietnam-s-charm-offensive-fails-to-stave-off-huge-trump-tariff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南部署了特朗普政府的攻击性攻势，削减了进口税，并发誓要购买更多的大型美国产品来保护其贸易依赖的经济，但未能避免避免白宫宣布的最大关税之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/vietnam-s-charm-offensive-fails-to-stave-off-huge-trump-tariff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:24:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普释放“火箭筒”美国关税时，中国发誓报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-hikes-china-tariffs-to-at-least-54-in-blow-to-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国在与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）迄今最大的关税受到打击后发誓要进行报复，这有可能使世界上最大的经济体之间的贸易陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-hikes-china-tariffs-to-at-least-54-in-blow-to-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:22:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普征收所有人，中国的利率将飙升至50％以上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-says-he-s-signing-executive-order-on-reciprocal-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统在一个世纪以来对美国最陡峭的关税征收，加强了他的竞选活动，以重塑全球经济和令人不安的投资者，这些投资者将贸易战视为对美国增长的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-says-he-s-signing-executive-order-on-reciprocal-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 20:16:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
